6 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
7 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
8 For the fiscal year ending June 30, 2027, the State Board of
9 Education shall budget all funds in the following categories and
10 amounts:
11 Category Total
12 1. Payroll, Salaries or Wages,
13 Including Tax-sheltered
14 Deferment Contracts and
15 Longevity Payments Authorized
16 by State Statutes $38,000,000.00
17 2. Professional and Personal
18 Services Contracts $36,787,370.00
19 3. Other Operating Funds $3,974,901,663.00
20 4. Expenditure of Federal Funds $1,000,000,000.00
21 TOTAL $5,049,689,033.00
22 The agency shall develop outcome-based performance measures for
23 each budget category.
