3 SECTION 12. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
4 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
5 The funds allocated in subparagraph g of paragraph 2 of Section
6 1 of this act for Early Intervention shall be transferred to the
7 Early Intervention Revolving Fund (Fund 250). It is the intent of
8 the Legislature that funding available for SoonerStart Early
9 Intervention Services be expended for direct services to eligible
10 infants and toddlers and their families. The State Department of
11 Education shall not contract, pay, or reimburse for administrative
12 cost recovery personnel, accounting, management information system
13 costs, and maintenance and operations at the state or local level or
14 indirect costs which do not comply with the requirements of Section
15 13-125 of Title 70 of the Oklahoma Statutes.
