14 Fund of the State Treasury for the fiscal year ending June 30, 2027,
15 the sum of Eighty-one Thousand Seventy-two Dollars ($81,072.00) to
16 be budgeted and expended in accordance with law.
17 SECTION 20. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
18 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
19 Of the funds appropriated by Section 19 of this act, Eighty-one
20 Thousand Seventy-two Dollars ($81,072.00) shall be transferred to
21 the Binocular Screening Revolving Fund created by Enrolled House
22 Bill No. 3016 of the 2nd Session of the 60th Oklahoma Legislature.
23 SECTION 21. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
24 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
ENGR. H. B. NO. 4030 Page 14

